definitions.definition: To name someone as a candidate for a particular role or position , including that of an office .
To specify in advance which pocket a ball will be potted in; to call ; to name .
To designate a peer (or oneself) as corresponding to a (potentially positive or negative) description.
To entitle , confer a name upon.

main_definition: To name someone as a candidate for a particular role or position , including that of an office .
